  "bio": "Adam Savage is a special effects artist, maker, and co-host of <i>Mythbusters</i>. In 2007, archaeologists at the University of Wyoming asked the Mythbusters for help testing the effectiveness of stone arrowheads. The experiment resulted in a segment on <i>Mythbusters</i> and an article in the archaeological journal <i>Antiquity</i>. Savage’s Bacon number comes from his cameo in <i>The Darwin Awards</i>, and his Sabbath number from performances with Paul and Storm at w00tstock.",
